                  </hi>, junior. I produce a letter which was given me by Benjamin Wolf—the whole of it is my brother's writing—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—" Dear father and mother—I am sorry to say I have done what I have; but if I have time, I will restore it. Dear father, I will replace it if you will give me time."</p>
